race.description: Apg - Vicbred Super Series Final Mobile Pace (G2)
race.comment: Smart mare KISS NZ (1) shoots for a clean sweep of the series and should get that chance from the ace draw. Came from there in her semi final last week and while she was beaten for early speed she still proved too good. Strikes at 50 per cent at this circuit and distance and looks to have the class edge. Her biggest danger could be SWEET IDEAL (3) who comes into this fourth up-and looks to be peaking at the right time having improved to go under by just a head in her semi final. Gets the same draw so could challenge. THE ANSWER (10) may need some luck from the back row but was brave in beating SWEET IDEAL to win last week. EUREKA JO (11) has placed in both rounds of the series and hasn't been out of the money when third-up so should be peaking. SWEETNIKKILOU (13) is another whose chances have been dealt a blow by the draw but she has been good in a heat win and a semi-final second and is unbeaten third-up so will be at her peak.
